PEOPLE ex rel. SMITH v. HAYDEN, Commissioner. (Supreme Court, General Term, Second Department. May 14, 1894.) Proceeding by the people, on the relation of W. B. Smith, against Henry Hayden, commissioner.

Argued before BROWN, P. J„ and DYKMAN and CULLEN, JJ.

No opinion. Order affirmed, with costs. All concur.
